Nhanganyaya kune TFF masisitimu

- Kupomba uye kusefa: Mhinduro yacho inoputirwa kuburikidza ne membrane module, apo tangential inoyerera inochengetedza zvikamu mukufamba uye inodzivirira kuvhara kwe membrane.
- Permeate uye chengetedza muunganidzwa: Iyo filtrate (permeate) inounganidzwa mumudziyo wepermeate, nepo zvikamu zvakaparadzana (retainer) zvinounganidzwa mumudziyo wekuchengetedza k

Iko kugona kuchengetedza inoenderera uye inodzorwa kuyerera, pamwe chete nenjodzi yakadzikira yekuvharika, inoita kuti TFF masisitimu ive sarudzo inosarudzika kune akawanda maindasitiri ekushandisa.
Kana iwe uchifarira nyika yebiotechnology, udza mashoko TECNIC chikwata kune mazano uye rubatsiro pakusarudza kubva yedu yakakura yemidziyo yeTFF, ine nzvimbo dzekusefa kubva pa0.1m² kusvika 36.3m²

Kana iwe ukatenga rezinesi rimwe chete, saka unogona kuisa chigadzirwa chedu pakombuta imwe chete. Ndokumbira utarise kuti HAUGONESE kuendesa rezinesi kubva kune imwe komputa ichienda kune imwe, kunze kwekunge komputa yekare isingazombo shandiswa mune ramangwana zvakare (kusiiwa).
Kana iwe uchida kuisa chigadzirwa chedu pamakomputa akawanda, une zvinotevera zvitatu sarudzo:
- Kutenga huwandu hwemarezinesi zvichibva pauwandu hwemakomputa aunoda kuisa. Isu tinopa kuderedzwa kwehuwandu kana iwe ukatenga marezinesi mazhinji panguva imwe chete.
- Tenga rezinesi resaiti kuitira kuti iwe ugone kuisa software yedu pane isina muganho makomputa musangano rako
- Kana iwe uri nyanzvi, uye uchida kuendesa rezinesi kubva kune imwe komputa kuenda kune imwe zvakasununguka, saka unogona kutenga rezinesi rehunyanzvi iro rinokutendera iwe kuti udaro.
Inzwa wakasununguka taura nesu kana iwe uchifarira kutenga rezenisi resaiti kana rezinesi rehunyanzvi.

Nguva yekunwa mash nemhiripiri chena?
Chinwiwa chemunga chine mhiripiri chena chinonwiwa mudumbu musina chinhu, kureva pakumuka mangwanani. Zvinokurudzirwa kusanganisa zviyero zvakaenzana zvevhu, uye tora teaspoon yemusanganiswa nekapu yemukaka unopisa. Iri resipi rinotendwa kuti rinoshanda mukusimbisa chibereko uye kuchenesa ropa, uye rinogona kuva nemigumisiro yakanaka
...
, vamwe vanoratidza kuti ginger, mhiripiri chena kana kuti nhema, uye mungbhinzi hazvikuvadzi kana zvikadyiwa zvine mwero uye zvine mwero. Mukuwedzera, bhinzi bhinzi, mhiripiri chena uye ginger zvinobatsira hurongwa hwekudya, zvakadai sekurapa kuvimbiswa uye kusaga.
Nekufamba kwenguva, vamwe vanoratidza zvingangobatsira bhinzi kuchibereko, sezvo inobatsira kuchenesa chibereko uye kudzorera basa rayo mushure mekusununguka. Nokudaro, vanachiremba vanorayira vakadzi kuti vatore panguva iyi yakaoma.

Zvikanganiso of Coluracetam powder (135463-81-9)
Coluracetam powder haisi chepfu. Saka inofungidzirwa zvakanaka-inoregererwa uye yakachengeteka.
Zvinokanganisa hazviwanzove asi zvinogona kusanganisira kushungurudzika, kuneta, kuora musoro, kutya uye kuora mwoyo. Zvakare, migumisiro yemigumisiro kazhinji inokonzerwa nekusawaniswa kwepamusoro kweeodotropic.
Vakawanda venguva yekutanga vashandisi veColuracetam mushumo kuneta kunowanzova mugumisiro wekutanga nepamusoro wepamusoro.

C ibhii rechitatu muduramazwi. Rinonbva kuBumbiro reMabhi reChiratini, rakabva kuBumbiro reMabhi eChigiriki, uye rinoshandiswa wo mukunyora mumitauro zhinji pasirose, asi harishandiswe muChishona shona pacharo. Bhii ra C rinowanikwa mumitauro zhinji ye Chibantu, senge Chindebele rinoshandiswa se bhii rekudzvanya.
Panoshandiswa C muchishona rinoshandiswa pamwe chete na 'H' - ch, saka mubumbiro remabhii eChishona (phonetically) bhii ra C hayiwanikwi.

Zimbabwe neMuvhuro yakaita mangange neAlgeria 2 kwa 2 mumakundano eAFCON mumutambo wakatambirwa munhandare yeNational Sports Stadium muHarare. Zimbabwe yakatombotanga yadyiwa 2-0 mushure mezvibodzwa zvainge zvanwiswa naAndy Delort na Riyad Mahrez.
Vakanwisa zvibodzwa zveZimbabwe ndi Knowledge Musona naPrince Dube. Nyika mbiri idzi dziri muGroup H. Algeria iri pamusoro nemapoinzi gumi, Zimbabwe ine mashanu, Zambia ine mana uye Botswana ine mana zvekare. Izvi zvinotevera kurohwa kwakaitwa Zambia 1-0 kuBotswana.
Kuti Zimbabwe ibudirire inofanira kurova Zambia kana Botswana pamitambo miviri yasara. Mitambo yasara iri kutarisirwa kutambwa muna Kurume gore rinouya.
Zimbabwe ichatamba neBotswana musi wa 3 Kurume apo Zambia inenge ichitamba neAlgeria. Zimbabwe ichapedzisira kutamba neZambia muHarare musi wa30 Kurume apo Algeri inenge ichitamba neBotswana.
Algeri yatobudirira kuenda kumakwikwi ari kuitirwa kuCameroon muna 2021.

Mukorezana
Shoko rokuti mukorezana (century in English) rinoreva kuverengwa kwemakore zana (100) zvichibva pagore rechi(xx01) panotangira zana racho kusvika pagore rechi(x100) parinoperera. Somuenzaniso mukorezana we19 chakatanga mugore 1801 chikapera mugore 1900; mukorezana we13 chakatanga mugore 1301 chikapera mugore 1400.
Pari zvino tiri muchizana 21 chakatanga mugore 2001 uye chinotarisirwa kupera mugore 2100.
Vanhu vekuEurope vakapamba Africa munguva yomukorezana we19; pakazopera mukorezana 20 Africa yose yanga yawana rusununguko. Ghana ndiyo yakatanga kuwana rusununguko mugore ra1957 , Namibia ndiyo yakapedzisira mugore ra1990.
Nokumwe kutaura tingaturikira tichiti mwaka wechizana.

Nhambwe
Muchidzidzo cheKupimanzvimbo, nhambwe (Distance) izwi rinotsanangudza kuti nzvimbo iri kure zvakadii kubva kune imwe. Nhambwe inopimwa nechiyero chinonzi mita - (metre).
Mazwi anodudza nhambwe[chinja | edit source]
Hurefu (length) - shoko iri rinoreva kureba kwenzvimbo kana ichipimwa. Kana tiri kuMasvomho, hurefu hunoshandiswa kududza divi rakanyanya kureba kudarika mamwe.
Hwasha (width) - shoko iri rinoreva kupamhama kwenzvimbo kana ichipimwa
Hudzamu (depth) - shoko rinoreva kudzika kwenzvimbo kana ichipimwa. Shoko iri rinoshandiswa kududza kupimwa kwenhambwe zvichitevedza rudzivo rwekudzika pasi.
Hukwidza (height, altitude) - iri shoko rinonyanya kushandiswa kududza kupimwa kwenhambwe zvichitevedza rudzivo rwekuenda mudenga. Somuenzaniso tingataura hukwidza hwendenge iri kubhururuka kana chivakwa chemudurikidzanwa. Mukutaura kwamazuva ose tinoti chinhu chiri pakakwirira kana pakaderera, muzvidzidzo zveScience zvakafanira kuti titaure pamusoro pehukwidza.
Mipimo yose yataurwa pamusoro inoshandisha chiyero chenhambwe chinonzi mita (metre).

- Processor yekugadzira: 1 GHz Cortex A9
- Ndangariro: 512 MB - 1 GB
- Flash Kuchengeta: 4-8GB eMMC + SD
- Zvakawanda-kubata
- Hapana kusangana ne desktop
Yepamberi nhanho ":
- Processor yekugadzira: Quad-core Intel Atom kana A9
- Ndangariro: 1 GB Min
- Flash Kuchengeta: 32GB eMMC Min + SD
- Zvakawanda-kubata
- Kubatana nedesktop (yakazara Ubuntu desktop ruzivo)
Pasina mubvunzo, chiitiko ichi chichareva shanduko diki munyika yeema Smartphones. Sezvatiri kutaura, kugamuchirwa uye zvinotarisirwa zvakanyatso kukwirira, uye kuti izvozvi isu chete tinoziva iyo nhau, sezvo ichiri kushayikwa kuti tikwanise kunakidzwa Ubuntu Runhare OS nenzira inobatika.

Kuongorora Vs. PenTesting
Pane nzira mbiri dzakasiyana dzekuyedza masisitimu ako kuti asaite.
Kuongororwa kwekupinda uye kusazvibata kunowanzo kuvhiringika kune imwechete sevhisi. Dambudziko varidzi vemabhizinesi vanotenga imwe pavanenge vachida imwe. A vulnerability scan is an automated, high-level test inotarisa uye inoshuma zvinogona kuitika.
Muedzo wePenetration ndeye yakadzama maoko-pabvunzo yakaitwa mushure mekusagadzikana scan. Injiniya achashandisa zvakaongororwa zvakawanikwa zvekusagadz
... 
na kune sisitimu.
Vulnerability scanning isarudzo yedu yekutanga yekuongorora.
Cyber Security Consulting Ops inogara ichipa mutengi wedu kusagadzikana kwekutarisa panzvimbo yePenetration Test nekuti inopeta basa uye inogona kukonzera kupera kana mutengi achida kuti tiite PenTest. Vanofanirwa kunzwisisa kuti kune njodzi yakakura yekudzima, saka vanofanirwa kubvuma njodzi yekudzima nekuda kwekodhi / script jekiseni mumasisitimu avo.

Bhodhi rekambani yeZimpapers Group, rinoti rinoda kutanga nhepfenyuro yeterevhizhoni nerhedhiyo senzira yekukudza kambani iyi.
Zimpapers ndiyo ine mapepamhau anoti Herald, Chronicle, Manica Post, Sunday Mail ne Kwayedza.
Pfungwa yekutanga kutepfenyura yakataurwa nasachigaro webhodhi reZimbabwe Newspapers, Va Paul Chimedza, kumusangano wekambani yavo wakaitirwa kuNyanga. VaChimedza vakati Zimpapers inofanira kuita izvi nechimbi chimbi.
Vachitaurawo pamusangano uyu, munyori webazi rezvekuburitswa kwemashoko, Va George Charamba, vakati Zimpapers inofanirwa kutsvaga nzira dzekurarama nadzo nekuti nyaya dzenhau dzepasi rose dziri kuchinja.
VaCharamba vakati Zimpapers inofanirwa kupinda zvakadzika munyaya dzekushandisa masaisai e internet. Nyaya yekutanga nhepfenyuro ye Zimpapers haina kutambirwa zvakanaka nevamwe munyaya dzenhau vava nemakore vakamirira kupihwa marezenisi ekutepfenyura munyika.
Mukuru weMisa-Zimbabwe, Va Nhanhla Ngwenya, vanoti kana Zimpapers ichipihwa rezenisi, vamwewo vanhu vanofanira kupihwawo mukana mumwe chetewo.
Mukuru weZimbabwe Human Rights NGO Forum, VaAbel Chikomo, vanotiwo Zimpapers haifaniri kutepfenyura nekuti mapepanhau ayo anoshanda akarerekera kuZanu PF.

Zvakanakira izvi hazvirevi kugadzirwa kwesimende, asi zvakare zvinoshanda kukongiri, dhaka, grouting, pendi, plaster, asphalt, ceramics, machira uye zvinonamatira.

Tinoita sei evhangeri mhuri dzakapihwa matambudziko ehufundisi atinotarisana nawo nekuda kwekukwira kwekurambana, vanaamai vasina murume, zvekunamata, zvichingodaro?
